[http://www.bamboocostarica.com/index.html Bambu Tico] has, for 29 years, pioneered the planting and utilization of [[bamboo]] in modern Costa Rican building. The factory near [[San Isidro]], [[Costa Rica]] grows and sells bamboo plants (more than 50 species), immunized material of different diameters (bamboo that has been chemically treated and comes with a warranty for building), and other bamboo products ([[houses]], kiosks, bungalows, offices, toys, furniture, lamps, etc.)


